                     <interp inst="t18240916-45-person435" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer of Marlborough-street, and received the prisoner in charge with the property.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. The gate was open.</p>
